This paper is primarily focused on object recognition using convolutional neural networks, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the impact of architectural choices and training data augmentation on the performance of CNNs, which are topics related to machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE).
